bodyEn:
1. My IMPS transfer of Rs. {AMOUNT} from {BANK_NAME} to beneficiary account {BENEFICIARY_ACCOUNT_NO} (IFSC {BENEFICIARY_IFSC}, {BENEFICIARY_BANK}) on {TXN_DATE} (UTR {UTR}) was debited from my account, and the beneficiary bank is showing a successful credit, but the funds have not reached the beneficiary. Please escalate to the IMPS settlement window and credit the beneficiary.

Attachments: UPI transaction screenshot, PSP complaint acknowledgement, bank statement extract for the debit.

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

bodyHi:
1. {BANK_NAME} से लाभार्थी खाता {BENEFICIARY_ACCOUNT_NO} (IFSC {BENEFICIARY_IFSC}, {BENEFICIARY_BANK}) को {TXN_DATE} को Rs. {AMOUNT} IMPS ट्रांसफर (UTR {UTR}) मेरे खाते से कटा और लाभार्थी बैंक सफलता दिखा रहा है, पर लाभार्थी को पैसा नहीं मिला। कृपया IMPS settlement window को escalate कर लाभार्थी को क्रेडिट करें।

संलग्न: UPI लेनदेन स्क्रीनशॉट, PSP शिकायत स्वीकृति, बैंक स्टेटमेंट अंश।

भवदीय,
{USER_NAME}
मोबाइल: {MOBILE_NO}
